{"type": "article", "id": 27183, "title": "混凝土宠物床", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-23T06:53:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 71, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702171506EJ2FMuj4g3HZ1WyD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>宠物床不一定要全都毛茸茸的才行，比利时设计师 Geerke Sticker 所使用的素材或许是最特殊的那一个：碗状的床由超高性能混凝土（UHPC）制成，通过三根纤细的木质床腿相连，看上去很像是小动物们栖息的洞穴。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171504R7tvkdyNwK0BYloc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171505OBdGWlZuYTrpQ2bL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171505gHov1YphOFyP8X5u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171505PvcyhUJa3MDCxBY8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}